content: I've actually been going to bed around 11:30 PM for the past two weeks, except for last Friday when I stayed up till 1:30 AM watching a movie. I've been trying to establish a relaxing bedtime routine, but I think I need to work on setting a timer so I don't get too engrossed in my book and stay up too late. Do you think I should try keeping a sleep diary to track my sleep patterns and identify any patterns or habits that might be affecting my sleep?
